div.div: Lee Hojae had given up his life as a pro gamer, until one day he received a mysterious message: Congratulations! Youve been invited to the Tutorial World. Intrigued, he enters the game and confidently chooses hell difficulty, but soon learns that he is trapped there. With a mere 0.01% survival rate, Hojae must somehow overcome the games agonizing challenges to figure out the real reason he was invited. This tutorial may be tough, but its secrets are whats truly hellacious. (Source: Tapas)

After being put on trial, the deity once known as "The Divine Twilight" is offered a job by Thanatos, king of the underworld! Now, the fallen deity is back on Earth as his former self, Lee Chang-Seon, and is tasked with sealing those trying to invade from beyond. With the promise of a fresh start, Chang-Seon is gathering the gear and skills needed to get the job done, but he's feeling some watchful eyes on him... Will this Divine Twilight see a new day, or is the sun setting on his second chance?
(Source: Tapas, edited)
